description: You can ask history wizard what happened on any  date of the year you tell Alexa, She will give you three events for the date you tell her, then she will ask if you want to go deeper into history. If you answer yes  she will give you three more events. You can continue this process until you interrupt her and say 'Alexa Cancel' or answer 'no' when she asks you if you want three more events.
exampleInteractions: what went down on July thirtieth
name: History Wizard
shortDescription: A history wizard that answers questions about the history of a given date
